OL,3,CCornwall MP's 'final warning' to South
OL,4,CWest Water boss over sewage pollution
OL,6,FA Cornwall MP says he has become so
OL,7,Ffrustrated with sewage pollution, he
OL,8,Fhas put the Chief Executive of South
OL,9,FWest Water on what he has described as
OL,10,F"resignation watch".
OL,12,FNoah Law, the MP for Newquay and St
OL,13,FAustell, has said he is issuing a
OL,14,F'final warning' to Susan Davy, calling
OL,15,Ffor her to take immediate action to
OL,16,Fupgrade the region's sewage treatment
OL,17,Finfrastructure.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
