OL,3,CCornwall MP's 'final warning' to South
OL,4,CWest Water boss over sewage pollution
OL,6,FSouth West Water has responded that it
OL,7,Fhas a 15-year delivery programme to
OL,8,Freduce its use of storm overflows
OL,9,Facross its network and redesign its
OL,10,Finfrastructure - but it also says that
OL,11,Fwork of that scale takes time.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country in
OL,14,FPentewan, the MP said: "The sense of
OL,15,Furgency just isn't there from South
OL,16,FWest Water.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
