OL,3,CCornwall MP's 'final warning' to South
OL,4,CWest Water boss over sewage pollution
OL,6,F"Getting detail on the timeframes
OL,7,Faround this infrastructure upgrade has
OL,8,Fbeen like drawing blood from a stone
OL,9,Fand I want them to be extremely
OL,10,Ftransparent with the public as to when
OL,11,Fthey can expect to see some of that
OL,12,Fchange which we've fought so hard for
OL,13,Fin Government and through the Water
OL,14,FSpecial Measures Act.''
OL,16,FHe added: "I'm pressing really hard to
OL,17,Fget that information on just when we
OL,18,Fare going to see those upgrades. A
OL,19,Ffive-year timeframe isn't good enough,
OL,20,Fpeople want to see action now."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
