OL,3,CCornwall MP's 'final warning' to South
OL,4,CWest Water boss over sewage pollution
OL,6,FAccording to South West Water's own
OL,7,Ffigures, there were 134 spills from
OL,8,Fthe water treatment works in Pentewan
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FElsewhere in the region, MP for
OL,12,FTaunton and Wellington Gideon Amos
OL,13,Fcarried out water testing on the River
OL,14,FTone in a designated bathing water
OL,15,Fspot.
OL,17,FThe result was a reading of 'poor'
OL,18,Fquality and the MP says water
OL,19,Fcompanies should be making cleaner
OL,20,Frivers a priority.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
