OL,3,CCornwall MP's 'final warning' to South
OL,4,CWest Water boss over sewage pollution
OL,6,FThe boss of Pennon Group and South
OL,7,FWest Water CEO, Susan Davy, received a
OL,8,Ftotal pay package of more than
OL,9,F#800,000 in 2023-24, including almost
OL,10,F200,000 in long-term share awards.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, customers' yearly bills
OL,13,Frose by around a third from April this
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
