OL,3,CCornwall MP's 'final warning' to South
OL,4,CWest Water boss over sewage pollution
OL,6,F"We are prioritising our investment on
OL,7,Fwhat customers have told us are most
OL,8,Fimportant to them and to help us
OL,9,Fdeliver on what we promised; to reduce
OL,10,Fthe use of storm overflows, ensuring
OL,11,Fwater resilience and supply, investing
OL,12,Fin vital infrastructure, supporting
OL,13,Fcustomers more than ever and taking a
OL,14,Fgreen first approach to our solutions
OL,15,Fas much as possible."
OL,17,FThey added: "We live and work in this
OL,18,Fregion and care deeply about what we
OL,19,Fall do every single day ` we are also
OL,20,Fcustomers of South West Water.
